Sentencas: Numerical simulation was implemented on a tubular solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) with indirect internal reformer used in the demonstration projects of Siemens-Westinghouse.
Titulo: Numerical study on the thermal characteristics in a tubular solid oxide fuel cell with indirect internal reformer

Sentencas: The Navier-Stokes equations and the charge equation were solved by means of a generalized, three-dimensional complete polarization electrochemical model for SOFC.
Titulo: Numerical study on the thermal characteristics in a tubular solid oxide fuel cell with indirect internal reformer

Sentencas: The distributions of both the molar fraction of gaseous species and the temperature were presented.
Titulo: Numerical study on the thermal characteristics in a tubular solid oxide fuel cell with indirect internal reformer

Sentencas: The characteristic of thermal energy generation was analyzed based on the simulation results.
Titulo: Numerical study on the thermal characteristics in a tubular solid oxide fuel cell with indirect internal reformer

Sentencas: The electrochemical process was exothermic reaction, which contributed 82.7% in the total heat generation.
Titulo: Numerical study on the thermal characteristics in a tubular solid oxide fuel cell with indirect internal reformer

Sentencas: The ohmic heat possessed 17.3% in the total heat generation.
Titulo: Numerical study on the thermal characteristics in a tubular solid oxide fuel cell with indirect internal reformer

Sentencas: About 47.3% of the generated heat in the cell was absorbed by the reforming reaction.
Titulo: Numerical study on the thermal characteristics in a tubular solid oxide fuel cell with indirect internal reformer

Sentencas: The air flow took away 36.6% the generated heat and the remainder 16% was taken away by the fuel flow.
Titulo: Numerical study on the thermal characteristics in a tubular solid oxide fuel cell with indirect internal reformer
